    {
      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "gookit/color",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "\ud83c\udfa8 Terminal color rendering library, support 8/16 colors, 256 colors, RGB color rendering output, support Print/Sprintf methods, compatible with Windows. GO CLI \u63a7\u5236\u53f0\u989c\u8272\u6e32\u67d3\u5de5\u5177\u5e93\uff0c\u652f\u630116\u8272\uff0c256\u8272\uff0cRGB\u8272\u5f69\u6e32\u67d3\u8f93\u51fa\uff0c\u4f7f\u7528\u7c7b\u4f3c\u4e8e Print/Sprintf\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u5e76\u652f\u6301 Windows \u73af\u5883\u7684\u8272\u5f69\u6e32\u67d3"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "gookit/color",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Tag-release"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "gookit/cache",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "\ud83d\uddc3  Generic cache use and cache manage. Provide a unified usage API by packaging various commonly used drivers. Support File, Memory, Redis, Memcached and more. Go \u901a\u7528\u7684\u7f13\u5b58\u4f7f\u7528\u5e93\uff0c\u901a\u8fc7\u5305\u88c5\u5404\u79cd\u5e38\u7528\u7684\u9a71\u52a8\uff0c\u6765\u63d0\u4f9b\u7edf\u4e00\u7684\u4f7f\u7528API\uff0c\u4fbf\u4e8e\u4f7f\u7528\u3002"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "gookit/cache",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Tag-release"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "gookit/config",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "\ud83d\udcdd Go configuration manage(load,get,set,export). support JSON, YAML, TOML, Properties, INI, HCL, ENV and Flags. Multi file load, data override merge, parse ENV var. Go\u5e94\u7528\u914d\u7f6e\u52a0\u8f7d\u7ba1\u7406\uff0c\u652f\u6301\u591a\u79cd\u683c\u5f0f\uff0c\u591a\u6587\u4ef6\u52a0\u8f7d\uff0c\u8fdc\u7a0b\u6587\u4ef6\u52a0\u8f7d\uff0c\u652f\u6301\u6570\u636e\u5408\u5e76\uff0c\u89e3\u6790\u73af\u5883\u53d8\u91cf\u540d"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "gookit/config",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Tag-release"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "gookit/event",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "\ud83d\udce2 Lightweight event manager and dispatcher implements by Go. Go\u5b9e\u73b0\u7684\u8f7b\u91cf\u7ea7\u7684\u4e8b\u4ef6\u7ba1\u7406\u3001\u8c03\u5ea6\u7a0b\u5e8f\u5e93, \u652f\u6301\u8bbe\u7f6e\u76d1\u542c\u5668\u7684\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7, \u652f\u6301\u4f7f\u7528\u901a\u914d\u7b26\u6765\u8fdb\u884c\u4e00\u7ec4\u4e8b\u4ef6\u7684\u76d1\u542c"
